	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="document" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/PAEPARD-Call-for-applications-for-support-to-the-development-of-multi-stakeholder-partnerships-that-promote-demand-driven-agricultural-innovation-and-research">Read more...</a>
